# TypeScript incremental build cache — generated, must never be committed
# (otherwise it produces merge conflicts on every branch merge)
*.tsbuildinfo

# Claude Code local session state (permission allowlists, task locks) —
# machine-specific, not project configuration.
.claude/

# AI-assistant-facing instructions — kept locally, not published. Anything a
# human reader needs (architecture, API surface, project layout) lives in
# docs/ARCHITECTURE.md instead; keep that in sync if this file changes.
CLAUDE.md
.vercel
.env*
